# 💰 AI Expense Tracker 

## 🚀 Overview
AI Expense Tracker Pro is a Data Science-based application that helps users track, analyze, and predict their expenses.  
It provides insights into spending patterns using data analysis and machine learning along with an interactive dashboard.

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement
Managing daily expenses manually is difficult and often leads to poor financial planning.  
This project converts raw expense data into meaningful insights and visualizations.

---

## 💡 Solution
- Track expenses using structured data
- Analyze spending category-wise and monthly
- Predict future expenses using Machine Learning
- Provide a dashboard for visualization and decision-making

---

## 🔥 Features

- 📊 Synthetic expense data generation
- 🧹 Data cleaning & preprocessing
- 📈 Category-wise and monthly analysis
- 🥧 Visualizations (Bar Chart, Pie Chart, Line Graph)
- 🤖 ML-based expense prediction (Linear Regression)
- ⚠️ Budget alert system
- 🌐 Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- 🔍 Category filtering
- 📊 Insights like highest spending & average expense

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python  
- Pandas  
- NumPy  
- Matplotlib  
- Scikit-learn  
- Streamlit  

---

